data.name: Pasta e Fagioli
data.quickTastyDescription: A hearty Italian soup made with pasta and beans, perfect for a cozy meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.
Add chopped onion, garlic, carrots, and celery. Saut√© for about 5 minutes, until vegetables are tender.
Stir in canned tomatoes, vegetable broth, and Italian seasoning. Bring to a boil.
Add pasta and cook according to package instructions until al dente, about 10 minutes.
Stir in the cannellini beans and heat through. Season with salt and pepper to taste.
Serve hot with a sprinkle of Parmesan cheese if desired.
data.modifiersForBase: Add beans for protein and flavor
